===ETAC中國法庭的判決===

2019年6月17日，位於[[倫敦|倫敦]]，由終止中國濫用器官移植國際聯盟（ETAC）設立的[[中國法庭|中國法庭]]（China Tribunal）<ref>{{Cite web|title=About ETAC|url=https://chinatribunal.com/about-etac/|accessdate=2019-12-30|work=China Tribunal|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200119034108/https://chinatribunal.com/about-etac/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，對中國政府強摘器官一案作出終審判決<ref name="Forbes20190617">{{Cite web|title=The China Tribunal Pronounced Its Verdict On Organ Harvesting In China|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/ewelinaochab/2019/06/17/the-china-tribunal-pronounced-its-verdict-on-organ-harvesting-in-china/|accessdate=2019-12-30|last=Ochab|first=Ewelina U.|work=Forbes|language=en|archive-date=2019-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191122022810/https://www.forbes.com/sites/ewelinaochab/2019/06/17/the-china-tribunal-pronounced-its-verdict-on-organ-harvesting-in-china/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。法庭主席[[杰弗里·尼斯|杰弗里·尼斯]]爵士（Sir Geoffrey Nice, QC）曾在[[海牙國際法庭|海牙國際法庭]]對[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]前總統[[斯洛博丹·米洛舍維奇|斯洛博丹·米洛舍維奇]]的[[戰爭罪|戰爭罪]]審判中擔任檢察官，他宣判了中國政府在強摘器官一案中罪名成立<ref name="Forbes20190617"/><ref>{{Cite book|title=中國強制摘取良心犯器官問題獨立法庭（簡稱「中國法庭」）裁決簡要|last=Nice|first=Geoffrey|publisher=China Tribunal|year=2019|isbn=|location=|pages=|url=https://chinatribunal.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/SHORT-FORM-of-THE-CHINA-TRIBUNAL-JUDGEMENT-Chinese.pdf|access-date=2019-12-30|archive-date=2019-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230220443/https://chinatribunal.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/SHORT-FORM-of-THE-CHINA-TRIBUNAL-JUDGEMENT-Chinese.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。審判中一個關鍵證人是恩維爾·托合提博士，他本人曾經被要求活摘一個犯人的器官。<ref>{{cite news |author1=呂苡榕 |title=揭中國活摘器官黑幕 維族流亡醫師血淚告白 |url=https://www.businesstoday.com.tw/article/category/80392/post/201904020008/揭中國活摘器官黑幕%20%20維族流亡醫師血淚告白 |accessdate=2021-04-27 |work=今周刊 |date=2019-04-02 |archive-date=2021-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426225851/https://www.businesstoday.com.tw/article/category/80392/post/201904020008/%E6%8F%AD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B4%